eed-know-about-tear-gas</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20141002/HK-gam1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20141002%2FHK-gam1_r.htm&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=b76ccac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20141002/HK-gam1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f8d592bbba6982586d80a54427301a39f3d15f57","tid":1425221,"uid":287887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"2014年，有研究指出吸入催淚彈平均8次以上者，長期出現有痰、咳嗽與胸痛的情況，是其他人的2倍至2.5倍[56]。亦曾有人因催淚彈的味道而罹患創傷後壓力症候群，而經常無故聞到催淚彈味道[57]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/催淚彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=0168ce6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/催淚彈</a><br />\n<br />\n但未搵到一d有更嚴重後遺症嘅報告"},{"pid":"72320913505f148d5b5fe0c562f45ff9be35e84c","tid":1425221,"uid":301017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38399c05357c83c3fbe26f9d3a3727805079cf6d","tid":1425221,"uid":287887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5c6e7752407df936e0a2a1410d0079d647d8a026","tid":1425221,"uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>別再送頭！三大招：擠提、機場、文宣</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426308</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撒資！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><s